 	<div id="main-article-info">

		
		
			<h1 itemprop="name headline  "
								>Miami, the great world city, is drowning while the powers that be look away</h1>
		
					<div itemprop="description" id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"                        	        data-component="Article:standfirst_cta"			>Low-lying south Florida, at the front line of climate change in the US, will be swallowed as sea levels rise. Astonishingly, the population is growing, house prices are rising and building goes on. The problem is the city is run by climate change deniers</div>
		
		
  	</div>

